px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--font-black); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\">2. Mathematical analysis,</p><p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-family: Montserrat; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--font-black); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\">3. Mathematical physics and functional analysis,</p><p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-family: Montserrat; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--font-black); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\">4. Differential equations,</p><p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-family: Montserrat; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--font-black); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; o